data.description: Welcome to this wonderful home in the vibrant active senior community of McKinney, TX! This cozy residence offers comfortable living spaces and is nestled in a friendly neighborhood. The highlight of this community is the recreation gathering space, where residents can socialize, relax, and enjoy various activities together. With its convenient location near shopping centers, restaurants, and amenities, this home provides both comfort and convenience. Whether you're looking for a place to downsize or seeking an active lifestyle, this home offers it all. Don't miss out on the chance to become a part of this fantastic community - schedule a showing today!
